com.viaoa.hub

Class HubMinusHubFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.hub.HubMinusHubFilter

  • public class HubMinusHubFilter
extends java.lang.Object
    A filter object that is used to populate a hub with all the objects from a master hub, minus the objects from another hub.

    For more information about this package, see documentation.
